<Page xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
      Title="The Eraser-Mode Menu">
    <FlowDocumentReader ViewingMode="Scroll">
        <FlowDocument>
            <Paragraph TextAlignment="Center"
                       FontSize="16pt">
                The Eraser-Mode Menu
            </Paragraph>
            <Paragraph>
                The <Bold>Eraser-Mode</Bold> menu lets you control the
                functionality of the stylus when the stylus is inverted. 
                The menu is identical to the 
                <Hyperlink NavigateUri="StylusModeMenu.xaml">
                    Stylus-Mode Menu
                </Hyperlink>
                except that the default item is
                <Bold>Erase by Stroke</Bold>.
            </Paragraph>
            <Paragraph>
                The inverted stylus does not work well in 
                <Bold>Select</Bold> mode.
            </Paragraph>
            <Paragraph>
                This menu does not appear when running the program on
                a non-Tablet PC.
            </Paragraph>
        </FlowDocument>
    </FlowDocumentReader>
</Page>
